---
title: Easy Sri Lankan Cauliflower & Chickpea Curry with Rapid Rice & Peanuts
description: If we had to list our favourite things about Sri Lankan food, we’d be here all night. But one of the best things is the variety of vegetarian options available – there are so many ways to make veggies and legumes exciting! This chickpea curry uses a mild yet flavourful spice blend, plus a dash of coconut cream to create a warm, comforting dish.
